Synopsis:
Your destiny is not predetermined nor etched in stone. It is not predictable or inevitable. It is not governed
by fate or providence. Your life is in your hands and you determine the life you are living now and the life you
will live in the future. By knowing this, accepting it as the truth and then learning the techniques and
teachings in "Living More Life" you will make it the best life you can ever live.
